      cases:[
        "Client-advisory copilots grounded in your product and policy documents",
        "KYC / AML document processing and screening support",
        "Regulatory and internal-policy Q&A across DE/FR/IT/EN",
        "Research and reporting assistants over your own market data"
      ],
      note:"On-prem or confidential compute · zero data egress · audit rights & exit plan documented"
    },
    {
      k:"Healthcare & Pharma",
      p:"Hospital AI fails in the review, not the demo. Special-category data stays inside your clinical network, integrated via HL7/FHIR and designed to your cantonal data-protection law — and deliberately outside MDR/MepV scope: no diagnostic or triage functionality.",
