      cases:[
        "Contract analysis, review and clause extraction",
        "Multilingual legal research (DE / FR / IT / EN)",
        "Drafting assistants grounded in your templates and precedent",
        "Due-diligence and data-room summarisation"
      ],
      note:"Privilege-safe · in-jurisdiction · your templates and precedent"
    },
    {
      k:"Government & Public Sector",
      p:"This already works: the Canton of Ticino runs a fine-tuned Apertus-8B translation service on its own infrastructure — 94% accuracy after fine-tuning on cantonal data. The same playbook applies to your canton or municipality.",
      cases:[
        "Multilingual citizen-service assistants (DE / FR / IT / RM)",
        "Internal knowledge and procedure assistants for staff",
        "Document and application processing support",
        "Accessible, plain-language communication drafting"
      ],
      note:"Runs on national infrastructure · data never leaves the country"
    },
    {
      k:"Insurance",
      p:"Your claims teams re-key data from scanned forms, medical reports and broker mail all day — documents too sensitive for a US API. We deploy grounded models inside your environment that classify, extract and draft against your core systems, as a FINMA-compliant outsourcing from day one.",
